<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pandas</span> <span class="kn">as</span> <span class="nn">pd</span>
<span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pickle</span>
<span class="n">warnings</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">filterwarnings</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&quot;ignore&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">testmode</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">False</span>

<span class="c"># Built-in dictionary for cutting words</span>
<span class="n">path_dict_for_tokenization</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;/Users/easonchan/git/jieba/extra_dict/dict.txt.big&#39;</span>
<span class="n">path_dict_for_stopwords</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;/Users/easonchan/Desktop/stop words freq list&#39;</span>
<span class="c"># Path of corpora</span>
<span class="c">#path_corpora = &#39;/Users/easonchan/temp/thenewslense&#39;</span>
<span class="c">#path_corpora = &#39;/Users/easonchan/Desktop/xmlOutput&#39;</span>
<span class="c"># path_corpora = &#39;/Users/easonchan/temp/UDNnews&#39;  ## only 3k articles under UDN news</span>
<span class="n">path_corpora</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;/Users/easonchan/temp/iterativeUDNnews&#39;</span> <span class="c">##20k articles under UDN news</span>

<span class="c">## Hyperparameters for training model</span>
<span class="c"># Minimun length of single document</span>
<span class="n">min_length</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">300</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="s">&#39;UDNnews&#39;</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">path_corpora</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="mi">150</span>
<span class="c"># Num_topics in LDA</span>
<span class="c">#num_topics = 40 if not &#39;UDNnews&#39; in path_corpora else 41 #=&gt; little bit better than 55</span>
<span class="n">num_topics</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">40</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="s">&#39;UDNnews&#39;</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">path_corpora</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="mi">100</span> <span class="c">#=&gt; little bit better than 55</span>
<span class="c"># Filter out tokens that appear in less than `no_below` documents (absolute number)</span>
<span class="n">no_below_this_number</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">20</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="s">&#39;UDNnews&#39;</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">path_corpora</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="mi">15</span>
<span class="c"># Filter out tokens that appear in more than `no_above` documents (fraction of total corpus size, *not* absolute number).</span>
<span class="n">no_above_fraction_of_doc</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.15</span>
<span class="c"># Granularity of model, may increase the model complexity, default is false</span>
<span class="n">full_mode</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">False</span> 
<span class="c"># Use HMM model for tokenization, default is true</span>
<span class="n">HMM_mode_on</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">True</span>
<span class="c"># Remove topic which weights less than this number</span>
<span class="n">remove_topic_so_less</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.08</span>
<span class="c"># Number of iterations in training LDA model, the less the documents in total, the more the iterations for LDA model to converge</span>
<span class="n">num_of_iterations</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">30</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">testmode</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="mi">200</span>
<span class="c"># Number of passes in the model</span>
<span class="n">passes</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">5</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">testmode</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="mi">3</span>

<span class="c">#Print all hyperparameters</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;testmode&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">testmode</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;min_length&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">min_length</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;num_topics&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">num_topics</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;no_below_this_number&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">no_below_this_number</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;full_mode&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">full_mode</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;HMM_mode_on&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">HMM_mode_on</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;no_above_fraction_of_doc&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">no_above_fraction_of_doc</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;remove_topic_so_less&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">remove_topic_so_less</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;num_of_iterations&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">num_of_iterations</span>
<span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">&#39;passes&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">passes</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">k</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&quot;Parameter for {0} is {1}&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">k</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">parameters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">k</span><span class="p">])</span>

<span class="c"># get stop words dict</span>
<span class="n">stopwords</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">get_stop_words_list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path_dict_for_stopwords</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">jieba</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">set_dictionary</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path_dict_for_tokenization</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">walk</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">os</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">walk</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path_corpora</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">doc_count</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span>
<span class="n">train_set</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
<span class="n">doc_mapping</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">{}</span>

<span class="c">## Start of preparing list of documents and tokens [[words_in_1st_doc],[words_in_2nd_doc]....]</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">root</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">dirs</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">files</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">walk</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">name</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">files</span><span class="p">:</span>        
        <span class="n">f</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">os</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">root</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s">&#39;r&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">raw</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">f</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">read</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="n">f</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
        <span class="c"># call preprocessing function</span>
        <span class="n">preprocessed_text</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">preprocessing</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">raw</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="c"># Skip document length &lt; min_length</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">preprocessed_text</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="n">min_length</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="o">==</span><span class="s">&#39;.DS_Store&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="k">continue</span>
        <span class="n">tokens</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tokenize</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">preprocessed_text</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">stopwords</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">full_mode</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">HMM_mode_on</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">train_set</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">tokens</span><span class="p">))</span>
        
        <span class="c"># Build doc-mapping</span>
        <span class="n">doc_mapping</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">doc_count</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">name</span>
        <span class="n">doc_count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">doc_count</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span>

<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;There are </span><span class="si">%i</span><span class="s"> documents in the pool&#39;</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">doc_count</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c">## End of preparation </span>

<span class="c">## Start of preparing corpus of docs, which comprise Bag-Of-Words (BOW)</span>
<span class="n">dic</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">corpora</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Dictionary</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">train_set</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&quot;In the corpus there are&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dic</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s">&quot;raw tokens&quot;</span>
<span class="n">denominator</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dic</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">dic</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">filter_extremes</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">no_below</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">no_below_this_number</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">no_above</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">no_above_fraction_of_doc</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">nominator</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dic</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&quot;After filtering, in the corpus there are&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dic</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="s">&quot;unique tokens, reduced &quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">nominator</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">denominator</span><span class="p">)),</span><span class="s">&quot;%&quot;</span>
<span class="n">corpus</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">dic</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">doc2bow</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">text</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">train_set</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="c">## End of preparation </span>

<span class="c">## Implementing TF-IDF as vector for each document, and train LDA model on top of that</span>
<span class="n">tfidf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">models</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">TfidfModel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">corpus</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">corpus_tfidf</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tfidf</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">corpus</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">lda</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">models</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">LdaModel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">corpus_tfidf</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">id2word</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">dic</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">num_topics</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">num_topics</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">iterations</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">num_of_iterations</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">passes</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">passes</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">corpus_lda</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">lda</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">corpus_tfidf</span><span class="p">]</span>


<span class="c">## Exhibit all the topics and related words</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num_topics</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;Topic </span><span class="si">%s</span><span class="s"> : &#39;</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">lda</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">print_topic</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">)</span>


<span class="c">## Exhibit visualization of LDA model in interactive graphic</span>
<span class="c">#vis = pyLDAvis.gensim.prepare(lda, corpus, dic)</span>
<span class="c">#pyLDAvis.display(vis)</span>

<span class="c">## Exhibit perplexity of current model under specific topic hyperparameter : k</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;===============================&#39;</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;Model perplexity : &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">lda</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">bound</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">corpus_lda</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;===============================&#39;</span>

<span class="c">## Save model output</span>
<span class="n">save_path</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;/Users/easonchan/Desktop/LDAmodel/final_ldamodel&#39;</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;Model saved at {0}&#39;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">save_path</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">lda</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">save</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">save_path</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c">## Save corpus output</span>
<span class="n">save_path</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;/Users/easonchan/Desktop/LDAmodel/corpus.pickle&#39;</span>
<span class="n">mappingFile</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">save_path</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;w&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">pickle</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">dump</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">corpus</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">mappingFile</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">mappingFile</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;Corpus saved at {0}&#39;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">save_path</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c"># Save document mapping</span>
<span class="n">path_mappingfile</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">&#39;/Users/easonchan/Desktop/LDAmodel/documentmapping.pickle&#39;</span>
<span class="n">mappingFile</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path_mappingfile</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#39;w&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">pickle</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">dump</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">doc_mapping</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">mappingFile</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">mappingFile</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;Document mapping saved at {0}&#39;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path_mappingfile</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c"># Save doc to topic matrix</span>
<span class="n">doc_topic_matrix</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
<span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">doc</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">corpus</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">dense_vector</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
    <span class="n">vector</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">convertListToDict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">lda</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">doc</span><span class="p">])</span>
    <span class="c"># remove topic that is so irrelevant</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">topic</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vector</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">vector</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">topic</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">remove_topic_so_less</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">dense_vector</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">topic</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">vector</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">topic</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">doc_topic_matrix</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">count</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">dense_vector</span>
    <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">count</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span>
<span class="n">savePickleFile</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;doc_topic_matrix&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">doc_topic_matrix</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">&#39;doc to topic mapping saved at {0}&#39;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#39;doc_topic_matrix&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
